因係紀念兩個人，一個是二十年代出任香港總司理的史提芬（AGStephen），另一個就係當時上海分行總經理施迪（GHStitt）。<br />\n<br />\n香港銅獅屬第二代 <br />\n香港滙豐創行於一八六五年，先後四座總行大廈均坐落於皇后大道中一號，上述一對銅獅在第三座總行大廈一九三五年落成時擔任守護神，他們由名雕塑家Wagstaff仿照當時上海分行門口的獅子所鑄，屬第二代。上海嗰對，則早在一九二三年在英國鑄造，出自HenryPooleARA之手。 <br />\n滙豐順風順水，史提芬及施迪功不可沒，大家估吓佢哋有幾重？原來一隻成二千二百五十磅㗎！ <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20021003/2866084\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20021003%2F2866084&d=EyvET%2B%2BaCRTqAKFB3QLIc9jU%2BfyVHSoZbIE78%2FWZKkA%3D&h=13a8daad\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20021003%2F2866084&h=3906fa11\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20021003/2866084</a>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-01T12:10:17.000Z","msg":"文章唔係話倫敦嗰對係香港嗰對嘅複製品？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-01T12:35:53.000Z","msg":"冇嘢啦 自膠<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f105af8cc042ec76ea7051ad3443772675b378b","tid":1806613,"uid":45206,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9338804861a37ca765154247b8f83efdde294636","tid":1806613,"uid":53026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-01T12:30:21.000Z","msg":"送俾日本仔好過"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-01T12:36:11.000Z","msg":"其實係<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/frownsmile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n支那，埃及嗰啲，真係擺係大英博物館仲好"},{"pid":"343b693cd9ef0134ea2e55705344d9e9270f970f","tid":1806613,"uid":38204,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-01T12:37:10.000Z","msg":"雷曼個期唔係都俾人噴過一次咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9177c50a5b04448988a9348fa687180b602b720e","tid":1806613,"uid":233156,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-01T12:37:10.000Z","msg":"不割"},{"pid